title: [Tiny Cove, Swimming Lagoon]
description: Surrounded by a protective ring, the swimming area is safe from boats or large aquatic life forms.  Pulsing with the push and pull of the tide as it curls into a frothy surf that strives for the beaches, the water is cool.  Moonlight plays against the surface and obscures the depths below.
location: Coral Villa, outside the island town of Mist Harbor
